The '''Queen's Pageant''' was a celebration that took place on [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]], the capital [[Planet/Legends|world]] of the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]]. The purpose of the event was to select the most handsome young man of those attending. Along with the [[Queen Mother]]'s [[Queen Mother's Birthday|Birthday]] and the [[Marauders' Masquerade]], it was one of the three most prominent balls of the [[Hapan]] year. The [[Preliminary Judging of Muscles]] was one part of the celebration.

The first such pageant was held around [[4000 BBY/Legends|4000 BBY]] by the [[first Queen Mother]], as a parody on the female [[Slavery/Legends|slave]] auctions that had been held under the [[Lorell Raiders]].

